Text:
I thank you, daughter ofson of
man. Your bravery will
not soon be forgotten.

I have a feeling we
will meet again soon!

Thank you! But now I
have to clean this
whole tower myself, kupo...
You will go no further, traitors.
Your every move is known to me.
I will rip the limbs from you and feast on your entrails!
And to think we were so close to Zenith...!
Gahahaha! I will lick the flesh from your bones!
Is this the end for us...?
I thought I heard the sounds of fighting...
How fare you, my young ones?

Lord Vedrfolnir!
Your presence heartens us all!
Well, look who joins the fray...
You will die with your precious younglings!
It was by your strength that we prevailed.
We have won the day, but there is no knowing when our foe will return.
Let us return to Zenith together.
We would be honored to, my lord.
This is the fate of a traitor!
We have done our duty here. Let us away!
You are so quick to retreat?
This battle was but a warning.
I care not whether you live or die, so long as you suffer.
You have suffered, and suffered well. Gahahaha!

Our foe's true target is Zenith...
We must alert the others!

I pray I am not
discovered...

I shall leave it in
your capable hands.

You fought well,
daughterson of the Land.
My thanks to you.
This does not look good for us...
It gladdens me to see you safe.
Now would be a good time to run, kupo.
Tch...! This is not going as I hoped...
Killing is fine sport. Being killed...not so much.
You have amused me for the day, my quarry.
But know this: I am ever the hunter, and you the hunted.
Flutter all you like, little one...
It will only make killing you all the sweeter!
No! I'm too cute to die, kupo!
What is this? My prey comes to me?
Yes, I shall slaughter the lot of you!
You will be my next plaything...
My playthings of late have proven far too...fragile.
I have not enjoyed myself so thoroughly in quite some time.
But there is more fun to be had, yes?
Ahhh, the thrill of the hunt!
A savage battle to the death!
The pain! The blood! The pleasure!
Is that all you have? Come! Come, I say!
It's as if the sight of blood urges him on, kupo!

Who are you calling “prey”!?
I'm no one's dinner, kupo!
This one's not right in the head, kupo!
I will not yield to you!
I will not be shown up by a mortal!
Perfect... These ones should make a good sacrifice.
These ones will play with you next.
Again? Are you good for nothing!?
Mark my words─your end is nigh.
My minions, I leave the whelps to you.
And here I thought they would prove more useful...
You are next! Do not fail me!
Is there no end to the dishonor you bring me!?
So be it. It appears I have no choice.
The weave of a shinobi's power!
To bring down a foe of such power...
Your strength is great indeed, mortal.
You fight well for a miserable traitor.
The day we next meet shall be your last.
For all his bluster, he is but a craven snake.
The next time I shall give him the death he deserves.
I'll tear you limb from limb!

Yoyoroon love loots!
Loots loots loots!♪
Your death shall come another day...
When next we meet, I will show no quarter!
You are no match for my minions!

My thanks,  !
I am at your back!
Darkscale! I have cornered you at last.
Your captains have all fallen to me.
This is my lair...and I have lured you into it.
You will not leave this place alive!
You are a worthy foe...for a traitor.
Face the truth, Darkscale! You are beaten!
O, Nidhogg! Give unto me your strength!
The crystals...! He drinks of their power!
The fire! It wells from within!
Now I shall smite you like the worm you are!
I cannot fall to this traitor...!

You know not what you do, Darkscale!
The power you seek will destroy you!
Gladly would I give my life in service to my lord!
I must have more power! MORE!!!
No words will reach him now...
Steel yourself. We face a desperate foe.
COME, AND I SHALL SMITE YOU!
Such power is mine, and still the traitor does not fall!
Give unto me all there is to give!
You only hasten your own demise, Darkscale!
GRAHAHAHA... I HAVE DRUNK MY FILL.
He has exceeded his physical limits.
What drives him to such madness...?

COME, TRAITOR!!!
I SHALL TEAR THE WINGS FROM YOUR BACK!!!
MY CLAWS SHALL RIP THE SCALES FROM YOUR FLESH AS MY FIRE CHARS YOUR CORPSE TO A SHRIVELED HUSK!!!
Alas, the proud dragon who once lived is now gone...
Consumed by power and hate, he is but a machine of destruction now.
Join me, mortal, and let us put Darkscale out of his misery!

I AM DARKSCALE, GENERAL OF NIDHOGG!
I WILL NOT FALL TO THIS TRAITOR!
I MUST HAVE MORE POWER...! More...power...
I take no joy in Darkscale's end, but at last, these halls will know peace again.
Till we meet again, O hero among mortals.

My claws! My precious adamantite claws!
Look what you've done to them!

Oh, you'll pay! Don't think
that you won't pay!

For your wanton destruction,
I sentence you to death!
...and his power grows with each passing moment.
But if not I, who shall defend the spire!?
I will not abandon those who suffer at Darkscale's ravaging claws!
It does not even scathe him...? Inconceivable!
No! I will not fall to this fiend who casts away his pride!
Even if I must give my life in the trying!
His power... It was too great...
YOU DIE AS YOU LIVED─A TRAITOR!
NOW YOUR FOUL BROOD WILL FEEL MY FLAMES!
KNOW YOUR TRUE LORD, DRAGONLINGS! AND FEAR HIM!

This looks as good
a place as any, I reckon.

Please, miladymilord! I beg ye!
Drive the beasts afield!

Now if I can just catch
something...anything.

The wife'll have me
head if I come home
without a catch.

All this thrashin' about...
There won't be a fish
left in the entire river!
The day is yours, but you have not seen the last of me.
You are a craven and a traitor both!
When next we meet, you will not leave with your life.
You'll not best me so easily!
I will kill you if it is the last thing I do!

Vileki─ No... Those aren't
vilekin... They're...

Twelve help us! They've
come for the bloody mint!

Keep that mint safe,
or we'll be elbow-deep
in vilekin as well!

The mint has sent the
things into a right frenzy!

Might serve us better if
we tossed the mint back
down to Ishgard...

At least they won't
be coming back?

Thanks for the help,
mysterious stranger!

Oi! Gundu! The whole bloody
lot of you are cravens!

Bowing and scraping for your
Vundu masters! How pathetic!

Like furious summer squall I
piss on the Gundu! Hear me!?
I piss on you!

Piss on Gundu!?
Gundu piss on your corpse!

As surely as sun rises and sets,
Gundu find and punish netherling!

Begone, dark ones!
These lands belong to Vundu!

Meddlesome as gaelicats!
Kill them all! Kill them all!

Netherling is strong, like a
dragon without wings.

The skies grow dark...
Kena Vanu will fight
another day.

As sure as the night swallows
the sun, your time will come...

For Kena Vanu, Vundu
would cast himself into
the swirling winds!

Netherling will pay for
sullying the white of the
clouds─in blood!

Infidels! You will suffer
the divine judgment of
the White!

To stand against Kena Vanu
is as a minnow baring its
teeth against the White.

Come, Skvader! Crush
these netherlings like
gastornis eggs!

The sun shall soon
set on you, netherling!

This island will fall from
the sky before a netherling
defeats Kena Vanu!

Foolish netherling!
Drink from the rains
of despair!
No, it will not end like this!
You shall join me in the abyss!
You lust for blood? I shall give it to you!
There is no greater thrill than the hunt!
Yesss, this is what I live for!
Nothing stirs the blood like struggling prey!
That I should be pressed so by their ilk...
I had not reckoned upon this...
Fly like the craven you are!
They were persistent if naught else.
We have wasted enough time here.
Darkscale is headed for Tharl Oom Khash.
Let us go and settle this once and for all!

Come, my young ones.
I will tend to your wounds.
To think that one of your kind could boast the strength to fell Nidhogg's trusted general...
Yet you have not tapped the depths of your potential!
Show me the strength by which you did slay the mighty Darkscale!
Yes! I knew that it was so...
The power ensconced within you is great indeed, mortal...
Yes, the power to make even a mighty dragon tremble...
I would see you harness your power to its limits, and beyond!
There is more power in you yet, mortal!

That's it. I'm movin'
to Falcon's Nest!

The damned things'll
suck me dry!

I've been cursed,
I tell ye!

Find a bloody chocobo's
arse to suckle!

I don't know how to
thank ye! Here's the
coin I promised.

What!? Miacids!?
All is not well!

The vile fiends are
befouling the river!

<click> <click>
You. Fleshling. Help me kill them.

<click> <click>
You win this day, miacids.
But the war is not over...
They are many, but we are strong!

<click> <click>
I grow weak. I go to inform the others.
Carry on in my stead if you can...
For the nourishment of our bodies...

Netherling fells my Skvader!
Rage swirls within me like a storm!

Gwahahaha!
Bow before the White, netherling.
I am power both ancient and unrivaled...
I do not bleed, for I am but strength given form...
Feeble creatures of flesh... Your time is nigh!

Wh-What in the seven
hells is that thing!?

Rain of shame floods
gobbie goggles...

We'll be back! You can't
watch the whole forest!

This one'll fetch
a fine price, I reckon!

I'll slice you up and
feed you to the bears!

I've seen baby chocobos
put up more fight!

Hah hah! If I don't eat
her first! Hah hah hah!

If ye see her,
grab her!
By the power of the Eye!

Drop your weapons and
you'll receive a swift death!

The Eorzeans
will pay for this!

Stay alert! The enemy
may still lurk nearby.

Do not forget
why we are here.

I think I may have found
something! Or not...
To think a mortal could wield such might!
Truly, there is no limit to your powers.

This battle is not over yet.
No, I have only scratched the surface of my strength...
You are possessed of great power─and the strength of will to control it.
It was an honor and a pleasure to meet you on the battlefield.
Farewell, hero among mortals. I will remember you.
I saw great promise, great strength in you.
Alas, it seems that I was mistaken...
Who dares disturb─? Oho, it is you.
I daresay this encounter is no mere chance.
If you would test your strength against me, I would be honored to meet your challenge!

There will be more. Do
not let down your guard!

We lay claim to this land
in the name of the Emperor!

You stand in the
way of progress!

Alive or dead,
the legatus cares not.

We will have to
report this to the legatus!

Illuminati brainfruit
is frontmost! Brings much
blastydoom to enemy!

None can withstand
ironfist of Illuminati!

Backwalk away or
meet oversoon doom!

Backgive whizzlepops
or feel oversharp pain!

Sound battlebells!
To arms, to arms!
I shall show you something special!
For the honor of House Fortemps!

Zundu must flee this place
on the wings of the wind!

Zundu legs are as
heavy as tree trunks!

Be wary! Cruel Vundu
trail us like a shadow.

Vundu surround us
like a choking fog!

Zundu feels hope, like a ray
of sun to chase the night!

My homeland greets my eyes
like a rainbow on the horizon!

Such treachery! Like a dark
 cloud on a summer's day!

At last, the storm is over
and blue skies return!

Here Zundu is safe as a
bird in its mother's breast.

Netherling is strong as wind,
and gentle as the kiss of
the morning dew.

Zundu remember your
kindness for many
summers to come.

Zundu feels a presence
behind like storm clouds
on the horizon.

Zundu hears voices, like
the whispers of the rain.

Zundu tires of being Vundu
footrest. Zundu just wants
to go home.

The beasts come,
roaring in like a tempest!

Vundu come, on angry
wings of thunder!
What is this? Am I saved?

My brother, you look as if
battered by raging winds.

Oh, what fortune! Like a ray
of sun breaking through the
clouds, you are!

My brother, your heart
seems as restless as
the stormy seas.

Were you perhaps chased
here by the cruel Vundu?

Worry not, for I shall guide you
home on a gentle breeze...

Come, and take shelter
under my wing...

Thank you, brother!
My heart shines like the sun!

Your breathing grows heavy,
brother. Let us rest here.

...Ahhh. The rest refreshes
me like a mountain spring.

Thank you, brother. Now let us
be off before the storms come.

Why rush? I see no
clouds on the horizon.

N-No! It was just the
rustling of the wind.

Finally! I thought spring might
come before you arrived!

Foolish Zundu. Time to
return and fulfill your fate
as a footstool.

You have escaped Vundu
clutches for the last time.

Proud, peaceful Zundu is
not a piece of furniture!

Netherling is a ray of light
in Zundu's darkest hour.

I must hurry back to
Ok' Zundu like the wind...

...and tell my brothers
of this Vundu treachery.

Oh, woe! Is there no
end to my dark days?

There are tracks
leading this direction!

Your orders are to
take no survivors!

You won't leave
this place alive!

Toss the bodies
over the edge.

The retreat is sounded!
Fall back! Fall back!

All for Tarasque!
All for Tarasque!

This one shall make
a fine offering!

Uplander must make
swiftheels with Slicktrix!

New vangob is complete!
Idyllshire is in danger!

Shkohhh... Slicktrix must
be telling shirefriends!

With a spear as stiff
as ice, I thrust!

Like the majestic
Coerthan puffer, I swell!

Like the surging waters
of the mighty Coerthas, I come!
Unauthorized temporal signature detected. Initiating elimination protocol.

This one shall make
an excellent offering.

My blood, my body,
my soul─as one!

Die, abomination!
The Fury wills it!

Here they come!
Protect the mint!

Zundu wants for water as
pure as the morning dew!

Zundu is as busy as a whirlwind!
Zundu wants for aid!

Like the clouds weep rain,
Zundu cries for water!

There must be more
around here somewhere...

What I wouldn't give
for a helping hand!
Hm. I could do with a few more.

That was too close!
Mayhap another time...
I knew the beast wasn't ready!
You'll be the envy of your friends!

The infernal contraptions are come!
Let us eradicate this threat to Thanalan!

Hearken to my words!
Glory in the song of rebirth!
We cannot allow these fiends to mar the celebrations!

This is an infestation...
Mayhap I should have brought more arrows!
We must stem this cold, metal tide!

They swarm in such numbers...
'Tis time for the stirring climax.
Do not let them...overrun the land...

Victory!
The bugs will not soon recover from this slaughter.

Thank you, adventurer.
The field is ours this day!

Their numbers are too great...
Let us fall back and regroup!
The faire is here at last!
Move aside! Let the lady pass!
You won't lay a finger on m'lady!
Let us grovel at your feet!
I just want to go to the faire...
Finally, I can enjoy the fireworks.
Please, at least pat my head.
Don't let her come to harm...
Why can Bugaal Ja not bathe at beach!?
You've been banned from the beach!
You jealous of bathing dance? I teach you!
Stop that! I've never seen such...undulations.
Smoothskins just jealous they cannot dance so!
Forbidden from hot springs, forbidden from beach...
But you cannot stop dance! Never!
Then dance out of my sight!
Heavens forfend anyone gets any ideas...
We'll be havin' our own faire!
You thought the Bombards were fierce!?
Thank you! Our guests should be safe now.
Don't let us see you near here again!
I will bathe, and I will dance!
Why...why do you despise me so...?
But I can't unsee his gyrations...
Now you see the power of my dance!
You are undeserving of my tradition!
If he returns, I may call on you again.
I can't pick these up alone.
Godsdamn, we'll have to try something else...
One sip'll perk you right up.
We can drink it right here.
Nothin' beats grog on the beach.
Come on, lass, I'll carry you.
Been itchin' for a little fun an' games!
Get your hands away from me!
Not the “fun” you had in mind, eh!?
Bend over and kiss your arse good-bye!
How do you like ribs? Broken!?
Gods be good, get the others!
We slaved away on those fireworks...
Intruders are too late! Too late!

Scamper all you will.
My lance will find you...
I shall pierce your very soul!
You defy the only rightful god!
You shall fall, as did your ally!
Our moment is come, Ser Janlenoux!

Now, Brothers!
Unleash the full power of the Heavens' Ward!

Lances at the ready...
Now fly!
No shield will defend you from the spear of my conviction!

Have you tested your tactics with Lord of Verminion?
Assemble your loyal minions, and come to Minion Square!

A Lord of Verminion tournament is about to begin.
Prospective entrants are encouraged to register at Minion Square!

A Lord of Verminion tournament is currently underway!
Prospective challengers are invited to assemble in Minion Square!

Lord of Verminion tournament registration will close momentarily.
Prospective challengers, please hasten to Minion Square!

Another thrilling Lord of Verminion tournament has drawn to a close!
The winners will be announced in Minion Square.
We hope to see everyone back for the next competition!
By what unholy strength have we been bested...?
But there is no time for talk. The crabs come!
I am reminded of a tale from long ago...
...Of fledgling adventurers who would fight crabs like these to better themselves.
I pray our training is as successful as theirs was.
I believe that will suffice for now.
Fighting alongside such a seasoned warrior has been educational.
I am grateful that you chose to accompany me.
If only I had taken a proper meal beforehand...
'Tis as if the very air is tainted by darkness...
Minions of the Shadow Lord!? From whence did they come?
These demons... They call to mind another old story.
To surpass his limits, a great samurai once fought such fiends...
Perhaps by defeating these demons I can do the same.
It would seem we have driven them back.
Alas, I could scarcely match your pace. This will not do.
There must be a way for me to improve more quickly...
It would seem we have underestimated our enemy...
But I cannot fail─not with so much at stake...
Look! Over there! Could it be...?
I know that fiend. Those jagged pincers, dripping with venom...
It is Serket, an infamous beast and slayer of countless men.
Come! Let us bring an end to its legend and see ours grow in its wake!
To think that we managed to defeat such a foe...
And yet...I find that there is something within me still wanting.
<sigh> I must find a way to overcome this. I must find my way home.
To think...my strength would fail me at a time like this!
I will not be denied. I will find my way back home!
On your guard! I sense a dark presence...
There! And it is not alone...
But I am not alone either.
I will deal with the dragon. Pray attend to the eye.
I-I struck true, and yet...it is unharmed!?
I fear I am nearing my limit...
No! I did not come this far to fail now! I will return to my world!
At last, my training is complete. And it is all thanks to you.
You were always there to keep me on the path.
I would speak with you more, but not here. Let us make for Limsa Lominsa.
A million souls sing to me!
Will you help us retrieve our rice cakes?
Observe how the cyclops swings his mallet before making your approach!
He'll pulverize the entire mortar at this rate...

A fine display!
You've saved our mochi─and the festival!
It's Ser Aymeric! He's come to kill us!

Execute the hostages!
The Fury wills it!
See to the hostages! I will occupy the rebels!
Lay down your arms or die by the sword!
Tell them to come to me! Now go!

Me may mah mo,
me mo ma me～♪

Ziggy biggie pretties time!
Ziggy Ziggy hey!

Ziggy super beam time!
Ziggy Ziggy hey!
Uplanders will make fine subjects for bloodpoison!

Someday we'll find it,
the─<croak>─
connection～♪
Ceruleum tanks filled... Burn them all!
Victory is assured! Do not resist!
None can stand against Illuminati! Resign yourselves to defeat!
Analyzing intruder combat potential... Selecting optimal strategy!
Initializing automated ley lines... Commencing metaphysical combat sequence!
Aether levels critical... Emergency shutdown imminent...

Not shiny! Not pretty!
Do not want! Do not need!

Pretty tower! Our tower!
All for us! Not for you!

Stay with the General!
Ul'dah! Ul'dah!

Gah! I swore I'd
see this through!
O Halone, lead us to glory!
System synchronization complete... Auto-clean is on standby!
All weapons locked and loaded... Commencing combat mode!
Recalculating combat variables... Switching to optimal combat strategy...
